{
  "stem": "10162.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So when I go back home, I'm going to tell my father, and they are going to give them something.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And also people who were very bad, so they will be punished.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know. good will be punished, then-- the good will be rewarded, and the bad will be punished when all this is-- all this is through.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was about six days or a week away west of the factory.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I didn't know until about four years ago-- it will be five years-- the details.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "About six or seven years ago, I got a letter from the mayor of Stadt Allendorf, of Allendorf, which we didn't know then that there was a town nearby.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We never saw a human being or a building other than the factory where we worked.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they tracked me, as well as other survivors, down through the Swiss Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I guess when we were liberated, they took our fingerprints.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And some day, it turned they were able to track us down-- not everybody, but most people, they were able to track down.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they contacted us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the letter said-- it was a very, very moving letter, that the school children in the area started a research project.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They want to know what happened in the outskirts of their native town, which was actually a village when we were there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Since then it became a town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It grew like the rest of the Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And one of the-- a history professor at the college was leading these studies.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they were trying to find out from their parents and grandparents.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But nobody will answer them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And this professor, [NON-ENGLISH], was leading the research.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
